parameters:
Lucia: Mother, I will definitely become a direct-line mage... just
like you...
Luuna: Lady Lucia, you were here after all. What's the matter?

Lucia: Hehe... It's the same as always. Mother won't pass on the
direct-line power to me.
Lucia: How about you? Do you think you can master the Azure Magic?

Luuna: Yes. The training is tough, but somehow I'll manage to learn
it.
Lucia: I see. That's good to hear.
Lucia: Luuna, I want to go to the lower world again.

Lucia: The lower world wasn't peaceful, but there were countries like
the Kingdom of Lyubel and the Free Country of Moduna that shared our
values.

Luuna: I don't know about the perpetually neutral Moduna, but Lyubel
was a country that had renounced war. Prince Reenu and Lady Lucia
would make a lovely couple~.
Lucia: But Prince Reenu might be a bit of my type~.
Lucia: Hehe, but too bad, I have Mido after all.
Luuna: Hehe... So Lady Lucia really likes Mr. Mido.
Lucia: Yes. Luuna, let's eat together once you bring the lunch.
Lucia: Now then, what shall we eat first~?
Lucia: What is it~? We're close, aren't we~? Don't hold back.
Luuna: Can I call you... big sister?
Luuna: Please forget I said that!

Luuna: I've been so happy since Lady Lucia picked me up. You've
treated me just like a real sister, and I just... I'm sorry for saying
something weird.

Lucia: Luuna, call me "big sister." I wasn't wrong in choosing you as
a court magician.
Luuna: Ahaha... It's a bit embarrassing.
Luuna: I'll call you big sister when I feel like it~.
Lucia: Ahaha, what's with that~? You're the one who brought it up~.
Luuna: Let's eat our lunch quickly before it gets cold.
Luuna: Lady Lucia, I'm happy to be with you.
Lucia: Me too, Luuna. I'm very happy right now.
Luuna: This is... a memory of Noah and me from the past...
Noah: Luuna, the floating continent is beautiful at night too.

Noah: It's strange to think that there are billions... no, more
magicians in this world. Those with the qualities of a blue magician
are even fewer.

Noah: When I was little, I decided when I met Luuna that it was my
role to extend Luuna's exceptional magical talents.
Noah: No, that's not all. I think Luuna is...
Luuna: I also feel the same about Noah...
Lucia: Luuna, Noah. You two are always together. Hehe...
Lucia: When will you two become lovers?
Luuna: Lady Lucia, did something happen today?
Lucia: Father is trying to form an alliance with Valentina.

Lucia: You know how the elite magicians from Valentina have come to
Jupiterino and are rampaging as they please, right?
Lucia: But Father can't stand up to Valentina.
Lucia: Even though so many of our own people are being killed...

Lucia: Mother, who is a direct-line magician, also values the
relationship with Valentina.
Lucia: As the princess of Jupiterino, it's frustrating... sad...
Lucia: There's nothing I can do.

Lucia: If only I could become a direct-line magician... I could
protect this country.
Luuna: Lady Lucia... are you crying?

Luuna: No... It's just that I've never seen you cry before, Lady
Lucia. I am proud of you for shedding tears for the people.

Luuna: Lady Luuna, Her Majesty the Empress... I believe Lady Reicia
must have some plan in mind.
Lucia: Is that so? But Mother won't give me any answers.

Lucia: I want to inherit the direct-line power from Mother as soon as
possible... and then those guys...

Luuna: Yes. Lady Lucia, I'm sure that one day you will become a
direct-line magician.

Noah: Lady Lucia, when that time comes, Luuna and I will lend you our
strength.
Luuna: Exactly. I too will master the essence of blue magic.

Lucia: Thank you both. I will definitely become a direct-line
magician.
Lucia: The three of us will always be together.
Luuna: Why would the Mirror of Truth reveal such information to me...
Becky: It's been a while since Lucia shed tears for the people.

Cain: Well, now Lucia is a legendary magician. People change when they
hold immense power.

Noah: Suddenly, I was overcome with sleep and saw Luuna and Lucia in a
dream. I thought maybe Luuna was having the same dream.
Luuna: So Noah saw it too.

Becky: The Mirror of Truth is amazing. It's incredible that its magic
reached Noah even from afar.

Cain: Noah, that's not really what you came here for, is it? You just
wanted an excuse to talk to Luuna, didn't you?
Cain: I knew it. You really do like Luuna, don't you?
Becky: Luuna, you should respond to his love call.
Luuna: Hehe... Noah, let's talk more when we get back.
Luuna: Now, let's get out of here.
